        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
Hi all and thanks for checking out this post,

I have a BIG BIG BIG decision to make tonight.  Do I spend all my money on a Circlet of Shadow?  I'm pretty sure on my server I can get it for 10-15k.  Problem: It would drain my bank account, and I really could spend the money to upgrade some items.

So the question is: 15k on a CoS or should I make following upgrades (check out my current gear in Magelo):

Froglok Bonecaster's Robe over Crystalline Robes
Shadel Bandit Ring over Velium Fire Wedding Ring
Oakleaf Girdle over Spider Fur Belt
Crystal Spider Eyes over Enshrouded Veil
Earring of Solstice over Electrum Black Sapphire Earring
Shai'Din Revenant Bauble over Electrum Black Sapphire Earring

Any thoughts would be much appreciated.  I would hate for CoS to become ND before I had one as well!

